Build an AI-powered course operations and content management application for a large online learning business with 2000+ courses.

This business runs multi-day and multi-module creative masterclasses such as resin art, candle making, silicone mold making, baking, makeup, soap making, nail art, pottery, and similar skill-based workshops.

Courses are often structured like:
- 2-day, 3-day, or 5-day programs
- each day may have one or more live or recorded sessions
- each session may be 1 hour or more
- sessions may be in English, Hindi, or bilingual
- recordings, PDFs, e-books, vendor details, trainer Instagram, Zoom links, WhatsApp group links, and materials are often shared

The application should be designed for:
1. internal course admin team
2. content operations team
3. student support team
4. marketing team
5. leadership reporting

The app should manage the full lifecycle of courses, modules, assets, AI-generated content, publishing, and social proof.

Create the following main modules/forms:

1. Courses
2. Course Batches / Cohorts
3. Course Days / Modules
4. Lessons / Sessions
5. Course Assets
6. Course Content Types
7. Materials Used
8. Products Used
9. FAQs
10. Transcripts
11. Student Reviews
12. Social Proof
13. Trainers
14. Categories
15. Learning Pathways
16. Landing Page Content
17. Automation Queue / AI Processing Status

