-----------------------------------
AUTOMATIONS / WORKFLOWS
-----------------------------------
Create workflows for:
1. when a transcript is uploaded, mark transcript status as uploaded
2. when transcript is cleaned, move to AI processing queue
3. when AI processing is completed, auto-fill FAQ, summary, learning points, beginner tips, mistakes to avoid, materials, and products
4. when course content completeness crosses threshold, mark course as Ready to Publish
5. when a review is approved, push it to social proof options
6. when a course is published, make landing page sections active
7. when a new recording asset is added, link it to the correct session and course
8. when admin marks content incomplete, send back to content queue
9. when batch ends, move it to completed status
10. when a course has no transcript or FAQ after recording upload, flag it for content ops

